<figureCitation box="[443,547,618,641]" captionStart="FIGURES 7–14" captionStartId="2.[151,269,1388,1411]" captionTargetBox="[205,1390,466,1342]" captionTargetId="figure-428@2.[182,1408,451,1361]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 7–14. Epeorus petersi and Eperorus gilliesi, larvae. 7. Dorsal view of abdomen of E. petersi; 8. Gill I of E. petersi; 9. Gill VII of E. petersi; 10. Gill I of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981); 11. Gill VII of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981); 12. Dorsal view of abdomen of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981); 13. Leg of E. petersi; 14. Femur of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268906" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5268906/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="394">Figs. 8, 9</figureCitation>
), tergal colour pattern (
<figureCitation box="[802,920,618,641]" captionStart="FIGURES 7–14" captionStartId="2.[151,269,1388,1411]" captionTargetBox="[205,1390,466,1342]" captionTargetId="figure-428@2.[182,1408,451,1361]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 7–14. Epeorus petersi and Eperorus gilliesi, larvae. 7. Dorsal view of abdomen of E. petersi; 8. Gill I of E. petersi; 9. Gill VII of E. petersi; 10. Gill I of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981); 11. Gill VII of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981); 12. Dorsal view of abdomen of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981); 13. Leg of E. petersi; 14. Femur of E. gilliesi (after Braasch 1981)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5268906" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5268906/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="394">Figs. 7, 12</figureCitation>
